Got to do one last sketch at HHN last night. This was one of the best years I’ve ever experienced, and I got to meet so many incredible people - Universal team members, performers, artists, photographers, and I got to spend it with all the people I love most. It was really hard to say goodbye this year, I also fell in love with the characters and was inspired to draw SO MUCH. Much love to everyone and I can’t wait for next year.👻🖤🤍 HAPPY HALLOWEEN!
.
